helpEmbed.description: CestnyTR is a multi-function bot with general commands, Admin commands, Moderation commands, Fun commands. Ticket and others will be added soon

publicCommands.description:
`/help`: Shows help menu
`/avatar`: Shows avatar
`/askGpt`: Ask a question to chatgpt
`/invite`: Give the bot's invite link
`/botStats`: Checks the status of the bot
`/mcStats`: Checks status of a minecraft server
`/serverInfo`: Gives information about the server
`/userInfo`: Gives information about a user

funCommands.description:
`/tweet`: fake-tweets a post
`/meme`: Generates a random meme
`/pixelate`: Pixelate a user's avatar
`/slap`: Slaps a user

moderationCommands.description:
`/ban`: Bans a user
`/unban`: Unbans a user
`/kick`: Kicks a user
`/mute`: Mutes a user
`/unmute`: Unmutes a user
`/purge`: Purges specific numbers of messages
`/setupLogs`: Setups log channel in your server
`/warningsAdd`: Add warnings to a user
`/warningsCheck`: Checks numbers of warnings a user has
`/warningsRemove`: Clears a specific number of warns from a user
`/warningsClear`: Clear all warns from a user

musicCommands.description:
`/play`: Plays a music
`/forward`: Forwards a music
`/loop`: Loops a music
`/nowPlaying`: Shows information about the current playing song
`/pause`: Pauses the playing music
`/resume`: Resumes a paused music
`/queue`: Get the list of your currently active queue
`/shuffle`: Shuffle current playlist.
`/rewind`: Rewinds the playing music
`/volume`: Change the volume
`/stop`: Stops the music
